Name: BIAS
POR Value: ADC buffer bias = 3; MUX bias = 4 -> fs >440 kS/s

Name: BW0
POR Value: RH1: sel2: 0; sel1: 17 -> upper cutoff 10 kHz

Name: BW1
POR Value: RH2: sel2: 0; sel1: 16 -> upper cutoff 10 kHz

Name: BW2
POR Value: RL_A: sel3: 1; sel2: 60; sel1: 16 -> lower cutoff 0.1 Hz

Name: BW3
POR Value: RL_B: sel3: 0; sel2: 0; sel1L: 17 -> lower cutoff 250 Hz

Name: LOWAB
Description: Select between RL_A and RL_B for each amplifier.

Name: STIMENB
Description: Stim enable magic word B. Enabled.

Name: COMPLI
Description: Compliance monitor. *Not currently implemented, register valye does not reflect COMPLI state.*

Name: LIMREC
Description: Current-lmited charge recovery switch state. Open.

Name: FAULT
Description: Fault current detector. *Not currently implemented, register valye does not reflect FAULT state.*
